@host = http://localhost:8081
@authHost = http://localhost:8080

### Login en el servicio de Animales (emisor del token); usá admin o consultas@papaws.com
# @name login
POST {{authHost}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "consultas@papaws.com",
  "password": "papaws123"
}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Veterinarios (Administrador o EncargadoConsultas)
GET {{host}}/api/veterinarios
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Servicios
GET {{host}}/api/servicios
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Productos
GET {{host}}/api/productos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Consultas
GET {{host}}/api/consultas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear consulta
POST {{host}}/api/consultas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "codigo": "CONS-0001",
  "fechaHora": "2026-06-18T10:00:00Z",
  "estado": "Pendiente",
  "observaciones": "Control general",
  "animalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "veterinarioId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "servicioIds": []
}

###
